---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Marina Costa - YA Author & BookTuber" description="Learn about Marina Costa, the 12-year-old multilingual YA thriller writer and BookTuber from Mallorca, Spain.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/8199574/pexels-photo-8199574.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=400&h=400&fit=crop" alt="Marina Costa" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-content">
          <h1>About Marina</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            At just 12 years old, Marina Costa is already making waves in the YA thriller world. Born in Spain to Brazilian parents, she's lived across three countries and speaks five languages, bringing a unique multicultural perspective to her storytelling.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Marina's Story</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>A Global Perspective</h3>
          <p>
            Marina was born in Spain to Brazilian parents and has lived in Switzerland, Brazil, and now calls Mallorca, Spain home. This multicultural upbringing has given her a unique lens through which she views the world‚Äîand creates her stories.
          </p>
          <p>
            She's fluent in Portuguese, Spanish, English, and Catalan, with conversational skills in French, Korean, and Hebrew. This linguistic diversity enriches her writing with authentic cultural details and universal themes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>From Reader to Writer</h3>
          <p>
            Marina's love for YA thrillers began with her voracious reading habit. After devouring hundreds of books, she decided to create the stories she wanted to read‚Äîmysteries that kept her guessing and characters that felt like real friends.
          </p>
          <p>
            Her debut novel, "The Infamous Disappearances of Helena Cross," was born from a simple question: "What would happen if someone in a small town just... vanished?"
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Fun Facts About Marina</h2>
      <div class="fun-facts">
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">üåç</div>
          <p>Marina's friends come from 17 different countries!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">üìö</div>
          <p>She reads an average of 3 books per week</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">üé¨</div>
          <p>Started her BookTube channel "Bookishly Marina" at age 11</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">‚úçÔ∏è</div>
          <p>Writes her first drafts by hand in a leather journal</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">üèùÔ∏è</div>
          <p>Gets her best story ideas while walking on Mallorca's beaches</p>
        </div>
        <div class="fact-item">
          <div class="fact-icon">üé≠</div>
          <p>Loves theater and often acts out her character dialogues</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-bg-light);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">BookTube Journey</h2>
      <div class="booktube-section">
        <div class="booktube-content">
          <h3>Bookishly Marina</h3>
          <p>
            Marina's YouTube channel, "Bookishly Marina," has become a go-to destination for young readers looking for their next great read. She reviews YA thrillers and fantasy novels, shares writing tips, and gives viewers a behind-the-scenes look at her creative process.
          </p>
          <p>
            What sets Marina apart is her genuine enthusiasm for reading and her ability to articulate what makes a book work‚Äîor not work. Her reviews are honest, thoughtful, and always encouraging to fellow young writers.
          </p>
          <div class="booktube-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>150+</strong>
              <span>Books Reviewed</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>50+</strong>
              <span>Videos Created</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>Weekly</strong>
              <span>Upload Schedule</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/watch" class="btn">Watch Marina's Videos</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .card h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .fun-facts {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .fact-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }

  .fact-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    min-width: 60px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .fact-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .booktube-section {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .booktube-content h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .booktube-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .booktube-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-light);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .stat span {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .fun-facts {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .booktube-stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>